Package: studyplanner
Type: Package
Title: Study Planning Tools for Power, Sample Size, and Cost Optimization
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Chunyu", "Liu",
      email = "cliu220@jh.edu",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Implements study planning utilities used in prior projects, including adjusted effect size computation for repeated measures (d_adj), two-arm power and sample size with baseline-follow-up correlation, grid exploration, and cost optimization under budget constraints. Includes a vignette and unit tests.
